Code()).isEqualTo(runtimeMarker.hashCode());\n        assertThat(loadedMarker.toString()).contains(\"customer\");\n    }\n\n    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n    public @interface MappingMarker {\n        String name();\n\n        int[] priorities() default {1, 3, 5};\n    }\n\n    @MappingMarker(name = \"customer\")\n    public static final class AnnotatedMapping {\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778138698021}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_0goWzqoQ1XCGQXUoipHFyYNq|fc_0ba4e5643502301c0169fc3e49a5d4819483e098cfc4370aa5", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\nplugins {\n    id \"org.graalvm.internal.tck\"\n}\n\nString libraryVersion = tck.testedLibraryVersion.get()\nString permissiveSecurityManager =\n        \"org_modelmapper.modelmapper.JavaDispatcherTest\\$PermissiveSecurityManager\"\n\ndependencies {\n    testImplementation \"org.modelmapper:modelmapper:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation 'org.assertj:assertj-core:3.22.0'\n    testRuntimeOnly 'javassist:javassist:3.12.1.GA'\n}\n\ngraalvmNative {\n    agent {\n        defaultMode = \"conditional\"\n        modes {\n            conditional {\n                userCodeFilterPath = \"user-code-filter.json\"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    binaries {\n        test {\n            if ((JavaVersion.current().majorVersion as int) < 24) {\n                buildArgs.add(\"-Djava.security.manager=${permissiveSecurityManager}\")\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n\ntasks.withType(Test).configureEach {\n    if ((JavaVersion.current().majorVersion as int) < 24) {\n        jvmArgs += [\"-Djava.security.manager=${permissiveSecurityManager}\"]\n    }\n}\n\ntasks.named(\"nativeTest\") {\n    if ((JavaVersion.current().majorVersion as int) < 24) {\n        run